metadata.description:
"I've always thought I think too hard..." ohh 21 year old me

The third & final release in my time capsule series for your ipod..."Crystallise" is a special demo from 2011. 

One of my earliest creations & experiments as an artist - a moody, pulsing, ethereal electronic track made in Ableton Live. 

At the time I was listening to a lot of Bat For Lashes, Feist & The xx...my early 20's were my formative years in finding my sound & path as an artist.
